title: Internet service provider market share in Australia fourth quarter 2013
summary: The statistic shows the Market share of Internet service companies in the fourth in 2013 .
Telstra 's Market share of the Australia Internet service Market stood at 46.3 % in 2013 .
gold: The statistic depicts a breakdown of the internet service provider ( ISP ) market in Australia in the fourth quarter of 2013.
The internet service provider Telstra held a market share of 46.3 percent.
The total number of internet service subscribers in Australia was at around 6.15 million in the fourth quarter of 2013 .
